---
import Section from "./ui/Section.astro";
---

<Section id="about">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center h-full">
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">About Me</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
        I'm a passionate C# developer specializing in creating modern web
        applications with clean architecture and best practices. With expertise
        in both front-end and back-end technologies, I build scalable and
        maintainable software solutions.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
        I have a strong background in software development, with a focus on
        delivering high-quality code and user-friendly interfaces. My goal is to
        create applications that not only meet the needs of users but also
        exceed their expectations.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4">
      <img
        src="/images/profile.jpg"
        alt="Profile Picture"
        class="rounded-full w-64 h-64 mx-auto"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
